Mint
================================================================================

Description
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Tiarra(IRC Proxy) に接続した動作することに特価した Bot

Require
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

1. net-irc
2. daemons


Usage
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

1. start

        ./mintd start

2. restart

    ./mintd start

3. stop

    ./mintd stop

4. config file change

    ./mintd start -- -c config.yaml

5. run on the top(not daemonize)

    ./mintd run

6. Usage

    ./mintd (run|start) -- -h
